13 An Act relating to administration of elections;
amending 26 O.S. 2021, Section 3-130, which relates
14 to post-election audits; clarifying language;
requiring Secretary of the State Election Board to
15 direct all counties to conduct post-election audits
for specified elections; modifying definition;
16 updating statutory language; and providing an
effective date.
