20 BE IT ENACTED BY THE PEOPLE OF THE STATE OF OKLAHOMA:
21 SECTION 1. AMENDATORY 26 O.S. 2021, Section 3-130, is
22 amended to read as follows:
23 Section 3-130. A. The Secretary of the State Election Board
24 shall have the authority to direct the secretary of a county
